headlines.description: — Giannis Antetokounmpo says he wants to produce with so much consistency that it causes boredom.
headlines.shortLinkText: Antetokounmpo has career-high 55 points, Bucks beat Wizards

events.name: Boston Celtics at Oklahoma City Thunder

headlines.description: — Oklahoma City's top scorer was out, so everybody pitched in to make things work.
headlines.shortLinkText: Thunder blow out Celtics 150-117 without Gilgeous-Alexander

headlines.description: — De’Aaron Fox made a driving layup with 0.4 seconds left and scored 22 of his 37 points in the fourth quarter to help the Sacramento Kings beat the Utah Jazz 117-115 on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: De’Aaron Fox scores 37 points, lifts Kings beat Jazz 117-115
